---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Astro Tailwind Starter Kit">
  <Navbar />
  
  <Hero 
    title="About This Template" 
    subtitle="Learn more about the Astro Tailwind Starter Kit"
  />
  
  <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-indigo lg:prose-lg mx-auto">
      <h2>About the Astro Tailwind Starter Kit</h2>
      <p>
        This starter template was created to help developers quickly bootstrap new projects
        using Astro and Tailwind CSS. It provides a solid foundation with pre-built components
        and best practices already implemented.
      </p>
      
      <h3>Why Astro?</h3>
      <p>
        Astro is a modern static site builder that delivers lightning-fast performance by
        shipping zero JavaScript by default. It allows you to use your favorite UI components
        from React, Vue, Svelte, and more while optimizing your site for speed.
      </p>
      
      <h3>Why Tailwind CSS?</h3>
      <p>
        Tailwind CSS is a utility-first CSS framework that allows you to build custom designs
        without ever leaving your HTML. It provides low-level utility classes that let you
        build completely custom designs without fighting the framework.
      </p>
      
      <h3>Features</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Fast performance with Astro's partial hydration</li>
        <li>Responsive design with Tailwind CSS</li>
        <li>Google Font (Poppins) integration</li>
        <li>Pre-built components for common UI patterns</li>
        <li>SEO-friendly with proper meta tags</li>
        <li>TypeScript support</li>
        <li>Easy customization</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>Getting Help</h3>
      <p>
        If you need help with this template, you can:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Check out the <a href="https://docs.astro.build">Astro documentation</a></li>
        <li>Visit the <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs">Tailwind CSS documentation</a></li>
        <li>Join the <a href="https://astro.build/chat">Astro Discord community</a></li>
        <li>File an issue on the <a href="https://github.com/yourusername/astro-tailwind-starter">GitHub repository</a></li>
      </ul>
      
      <h3>License</h3>
      <p>
        This template is open-source and available under the MIT License. Feel free to use it
        for personal or commercial projects.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>